Ms. Amita is here!

172
00:08:47,120 --> 00:08:47,600
Ms. Amita.

173
00:08:49,600 --> 00:08:50,150
Ms. Amita.

174
00:08:52,150 --> 00:08:53,080
Inspector He said

175
00:08:53,550 --> 00:08:54,150
court assembly

176
00:08:54,150 --> 00:08:55,750
is suspended
due to Mr. Li's experiment.

177
00:08:55,910 --> 00:08:57,600
To ensure Hu merchants' interests,

178
00:08:57,644 --> 00:09:00,555
Hu Merchants' Association must
personally supervise this experiment.

179
00:09:00,644 --> 00:09:02,000
How come I haven't heard of it?

180
00:09:02,960 --> 00:09:03,720
Mr. Li.

181
00:09:05,030 --> 00:09:05,960
Inspector He said

182
00:09:06,022 --> 00:09:08,200
you and the horses
have been exhausted for days.

183
00:09:08,750 --> 00:09:09,390
He ordered me

184
00:09:09,390 --> 00:09:10,600
to give you some fine horses.

185
00:09:14,630 --> 00:09:15,790
If the experiment fails,

186
00:09:15,844 --> 00:09:16,870
you can't get away with it

187
00:09:16,870 --> 00:09:17,790
just by saying

188
00:09:18,910 --> 00:09:20,030
there are no more horses.

189
00:09:22,120 --> 00:09:23,120
As for the riders,

190
00:09:23,320 --> 00:09:25,444
do you think we're qualified for it?

191
00:09:29,840 --> 00:09:30,670
Are you serious?

192
00:09:31,670 --> 00:09:34,480
Your riders have been riding for days.

193
00:09:34,480 --> 00:09:35,870
They're already exhausted.

194
00:09:36,840 --> 00:09:38,444
If they continue to hold on like this,

195
00:09:38,600 --> 00:09:40,030
someone will probably die.

196
00:09:40,630 --> 00:09:41,750
You're right.

197
00:09:44,840 --> 00:09:46,030
The experiment continues!

198
00:09:46,030 --> 00:09:49,440
- Alright!
- Alright!

199
00:09:49,720 --> 00:09:53,150
- Alright!
- Alright!

200
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:55,240
She's clearly

201
00:09:55,240 --> 00:09:56,910
trying to go against me.

202
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:01,200
Tell me

203
00:10:02,240 --> 00:10:04,030
if Amita

204
00:10:04,910 --> 00:10:06,120
hasn't gotten over

205
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:08,200
the dagger incident.

206
00:10:08,840 --> 00:10:10,422
You misunderstood her, Inspector He.

207
00:10:10,750 --> 00:10:12,000
Ms. Amita sent horses this time

208
00:10:12,000 --> 00:10:14,066
because she knew
that the litchis' smell had changed.

209
00:10:14,111 --> 00:10:15,733
Its taste will change overnight.

210
00:10:15,910 --> 00:10:17,870
This experiment is doomed to fail.

211
00:10:18,750 --> 00:10:19,480
That's why

212
00:10:19,750 --> 00:10:21,320
Ms. Amita sent the horses

213
00:10:21,320 --> 00:10:22,360
in your name.

214
00:10:22,870 --> 00:10:24,790
First, it can show

215
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:25,960
your generosity

216
00:10:26,150 --> 00:10:27,600
and concern for His Majesty.

217
00:10:28,240 --> 00:10:29,000
Second,

218
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:30,630
it can also shut Li Shande up

219
00:10:31,200 --> 00:10:32,720
and prevent him from using

220
00:10:32,720 --> 00:10:34,240
the lack of horses as an excuse

221
00:10:34,240 --> 00:10:35,840
for the failure of the experiment.

222
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:36,840
It'll eliminate

223
00:10:36,840 --> 00:10:38,870
his idea of ​​raising money
to change his luck.

224
00:10:39,200 --> 00:10:41,240
This will be
killing two birds with one stone.

225
00:10:46,600 --> 00:10:48,270
Have you been to Small East Gate?

226
00:10:49,030 --> 00:10:52,000
Is this experiment really failing?

227
