and leaking juice within one day.

229
00:10:58,390 --> 00:10:59,240
That's good.

230
00:11:00,240 --> 00:11:02,720
I will go to Small East Gate tomorrow

231
00:11:03,600 --> 00:11:06,390
as a farewell to Li Shande.

232
00:11:07,030 --> 00:11:08,320
It's an honor for Li Shande

233
00:11:08,320 --> 00:11:09,630
to have your presence.

234
00:11:10,390 --> 00:11:12,911
I shall now take my leave.

235
00:11:21,030 --> 00:11:21,733
Inspector He.

236
00:11:22,600 --> 00:11:24,000
After Amita went there,

237
00:11:24,360 --> 00:11:25,790
she became inseparable

238
00:11:26,066 --> 00:11:27,120
from that darn soldier.

239
00:11:27,550 --> 00:11:28,790
It's hard to do anything.

240
00:11:30,000 --> 00:11:32,790
